com.buschmais.xo.impl

Class AbstractInstanceManager<DatastoreId,DatastoreType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.buschmais.xo.impl.AbstractInstanceManager<DatastoreId,DatastoreType>
  • Type Parameters:
    DatastoreId - The id type of the datastore type.
    DatastoreType - The datastore type.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EntityInstanceManager, RelationInstanceManager

    public abstract class AbstractInstanceManager<DatastoreId,DatastoreType>
extends Object
    Abstract base implementation of an instance manager.

    It provides functionality to map the lifecycle of proxy instances to their corresponding datastore type.
